channel.title: Cache Error
channel.description:
Hey I just uploaded a new cache to dropbox and delted my old cache. Before I had my cache in my client folder and in my C: drive, I took the cache out of my client folder and changed the link in the cachedownloader.java, now whenever I run my client, it doesn't even try to download the cache, it downloads the old one but doesn't work, can anyone help? this is the error btw
HaizScape is loading.. java.io.FileNotFoundException: nullMaps\mapConfig.txt (The system cannot find th e path specified) at java.io.FileInputStream.open(Native Method) at java.io.FileInputStream.(FileInputStream.java:138) at java.io.FileInputStream.(FileInputStream.java:97) at java.io.FileReader.(FileReader.java:58) at client.setNewMaps(client.java:81) at client.startUp(client.java:8866) at RSApplet.run(RSApplet.java:33) at client.run(client.java:6074) at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:722) java.lang.NullPointerException at java.io.File.(File.java:251) at Update.(Update.java:25) at client.streamLoaderForName(client.java:4778) at client.startUp(client.java:8876) at RSApplet.run(RSApplet.java:33) at client.run(client.java:6074) at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:722)
